🎰 1 in Las Vegas
#️⃣ #aftersicecream #milkybun
👇 WE CATER

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Afters Ice Cream in Afters Ice Cream with @tryitordiet, and @dailyfoodfeed. May be an image of dessert.

node.text: Try our new milkshakes made with any of our ice cream flavors! 🥤🍨 Available at most locations or get it delivered locally at aftersicecream.com or any major delivery app 🚗 #aftersicecream

node.text:
Happy #NationalIceCreamDay!🍦 Here's a look at our new Las Vegas location at @virginhotelslv made by @dailyfoodfeed 👀 Come by this location anytime until midnight today and get a free pair of Afters Sunglasses when you spend over $20 while supplies last! 😎
———
For ALL LOCATIONS today only, get a FREE scoop when you buy a pint or 2 FREE scoops with a quart.
📸: @dailyfoodfeed

NEW FLAVOR: Blueberry Donut Ice Cream 🫐🍩🍨 We’re celebrating #NationalIceCreamDay tomorrow Sunday 7/18 BIG with the release of this new flavor (all made in-house down to the donuts) at all locations!🍦 Tomorrow only, get yourself a pint of any flavor and you can get a scoop of this (or any flavor) FREE at any location. Last… Our Las Vegas @virginhotelslv is officially opening! 🎈 We’ll be giving away a free Afters tee with purchase of a scoop or more to our first 50 customers starting at noon only at our new Las Vegas location 🥳 Get your ice cream in a cup, cone, pint/quart or in our famous #MilkyBun! 🍩 Who’s celebrating with us?! #aftersicecream

In-store only. While supplies last. Limit 1 offer per person.
